to this place is admirable,

638
00:42:40,161 --> 00:42:43,496
but you're young
and you're rash.

639
00:42:43,564 --> 00:42:46,066
<i>Show everyone your motive here</i>
<i>is for the common good.</i>

640
00:42:46,133 --> 00:42:48,301
