00:45:56,056 --> 00:45:59,826
<i>Mr. Guthrie's orders</i>
<i>were explicit.</i>

668
00:45:59,894 --> 00:46:03,763
No matter what, I was to make sure
that you were on this ship.

669
00:46:03,831 --> 00:46:05,865
