00:47:44,965 --> 00:47:46,299
She chose it.

685
00:47:46,367 --> 00:47:49,903
"She chose it"?

686
00:47:49,970 --> 00:47:53,239
"She chose it."

687
00:47:53,307 --> 00:47:55,174
I've been repeating
those words to myself

688
00:47:55,242 --> 00:47:58,678
