00:48:43,424 --> 00:48:45,858
To be perfectly honest,
I don't care

702
00:48:45,926 --> 00:48:47,860
because the moment
I start making choices

703
00:48:47,928 --> 00:48:49,762
based on her decisions,

704
00:48:49,830 --> 00:48:52,332
