that you've requested a skiff?

714
00:49:27,334 --> 00:49:29,435
I suppose that's
none of my business,

715
00:49:29,503 --> 00:49:33,606
but you do realize that we may be able
to hunt again soon.

716
00:49:33,674 --> 00:49:36,009
